import React, {Fragment, Component } from 'react'

export class adminBarChart extends Component {
  render() {
      const data = [
        {month : 'January', value: 500},
        {month : 'February', value: 100},
        {month : 'March', value: 200},
        {month : 'April', value: 1},
        {month : 'May', value: 50},
        {month : 'June', value: 500},
        {month : 'July', value: 500},
        {month : 'Augest', value: 500},
        {month : 'Oectober', value: 500},
        {month : 'Novmber', value: 500},
        {month : 'December', value: 500},
      ];
    return (
    <Fragment>
    <LineChart width={500} height={300} data={data}>
    <XAxis dataKey="month"/>
    <YAxis/>
    <CartesianGrid stroke="#eee" strokeDasharray="5 5"/>
    <Line type="monotone" dataKey="uv" stroke="#8884d8" />
    <Line type="monotone" dataKey="pv" stroke="#82ca9d" />
    </LineChart>
    </Fragment>    
    )
  }
}

export default adminBarChart
